Install Angular CLI via Cmd Prompt
  npm install -g @angular/cli

Create New Project
  ng new tss


Install JS packages
  npm install jquery --save
  npm install bootstrap --save


Run Development Server
  ng serve

Build For Production
  ng build --prod

Generate Component
  ng generate component xyz

Add Dependancy
  ng add _____
  ng add @angular/material

Run and Watch Tests????
  ng test

Import Forms Module
  import { FormsModule } from '@angular/forms'; inside app.module.ts (NgModel lives here)
  Add FormsModule in the imports array
